## Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Not using `protectedProcedure` | Protect sensitive routes |
| Forgetting `superjson` | Add transformer for dates/BigInt |
| Direct Prisma in components | Use tRPC procedures |
| Not invalidating queries | Call `utils.*.invalidate()` |
| Missing `@@index` | Add indexes for foreign keys |
| Exposing server code | Keep server code in `src/server/` |
